<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Note: Certain splinter sects, such as the Church of Maxwellism, generally view Sarkicism as either destroyed thousands of years ago or as simply an allegory for the &quot;imperfection&quot; of organic life and for those who are &quot;tethered&quot; to their base, biological nature.</div>
